\c 5
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti afambiswe zvakanaka pakati pevavengi vake
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba; nenehiroti. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ipai nzeve kumashoko angu, Jehovha, mucherekedze kuzvidya moyo kwangu\x + Map. 39.3.\x*.
\v 2 Teererai kuinzwi rekuchema kwangu, mambo wangu naMwari wangu\x + Map. 84.3.\x*; nokuti kwamuri ndinonyengetera\x + Map. 65.2.\x*.
\v 3 Muchanzwa inzwi rangu mangwanani, Jehovha\x + Map. 30.5. 88.13. 90.14. 130.6. 143.8. Map. 46.5. 119.147.\x*; mangwanani ndichakurongedzerai\x + Job. 33.5. Map. 50.21.\x* \add munyengetero wangu\add*, ndichirindira\x + Mik. 7.7.\x*.
\v 4 Nokuti hamusi Mwari anofara muzvakaipa; wakaipa haangagari nemwi.
\v 5 Vanozvikudza havangazvimisi pamberi pemeso enyu; munovenga vese vaiti vezvakaipa\x + Map. 73.3. 75.4. Habh. 1.13.\x*.
\v 6 Muchaparadza vanotaura nhema. Jehovha anosema munhu weropa neunyengeri\x + Map. 4.2. Zvak. 21.8. 22.15.\x*.
\v 7 Asi kana ndiri ini, ndichapinda muimba yenyu mukuwanda kwengoni dzenyu; ndichashumira\x + Map. 132.7.\x* ndakananga kutembere yenyu tsvene mukukutyai\x + 1 Madz. 8.29,30. Map. 132.7.\x*.
\v 8 Nditungamirirei, Jehovha, mukururama kwenyu nekuda kwevavengi vangu\x + Map. 23.3. 25.4.\x*; ruramisai nzira yenyu pamberi pangu\x + Ezi. 8.21.\x*.
\v 9 Nokuti hapana uchokwadi pamuromo wavo; mukati mavo uipi\x + Map. 49.11.\x*; huro yavo\x + VaRom. 3.13.\x* iguva rakashama\x + Jer. 5.16.\x*; vanobata kumeso nerurimi rwavo\x + Zvir. 2.16. 7.5. Map. 12.2. Map. 36.2.\x*.
\v 10 Muti vane mhosva, Mwari. Ngavawe nemano avo; muvarase nekuda kweuwandu hwezvitadzo zvavo, nokuti vakakumukirai.
\v 11 Asi ngavafare\x + Isa. 65.13.\x* vese vanovimba nemwi\x + Map. 2.12.\x*; ngavadanidzire nguva dzose nemufaro, nokuti munovadzivirira; nevanoda zita renyu ngavafare mamuri\x + 1 Sam. 2.1. Map. 9.2.\x*.
\v 12 Nokuti imwi Jehovha mucharopafadza wakarurama; muchamukomberedza nenyasha senhovo huru\x + Map. 35.2.\x*.